title: Grateful Dead Live at Reunion Arena on 1988-10-21
description:
Set 1

Let The Good Times Roll, Feel Like A Stranger-> Franklin's Tower, Walkin' Blues, Believe It Or Not, Memphis Blues, Dupree's Diamond Blues, Jack Straw

Set 2

Wang Dang Doodle, Victim Or The Crime-> Foolish Heart, Women Are Smarter-> Drums-> Space-> I Will Take You Home-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> All Along The Watchtower-> Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Brokedown Palace

Happy B-Day sung before Wang Dang (Brent's 36th)
